import { GridItem, Heading, Stack } from '@chakra-ui/layout'
import React from 'react'

import AspectCard from './AspectCard'
function Homepage() {
  return (
    <GridItem colSpan={4}>
      <Heading> The Classical Maya </Heading>
      <GridItem colStart={2}></GridItem>
      <Stack direction='row' spacing={6}>
        <AspectCard />
        <AspectCard />
      </Stack>
      <Stack direction='row' spacing={6}>
        <AspectCard />
        <AspectCard />
      </Stack>
    </GridItem>
  )
}

export default Homepage
